2007年11月，《怪异同床人》的制片人采取了法律措施，控告环球电影公司侵犯版权。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/film/filmmakers-take-on-hollywood-over-comedy-copy/2007/11/23/1195753303752.html | title=Filmmakers take on Hollywood over comedy 'copy' | publisher=''[[雪梨晨鋒報|雪梨晨鋒報]]'' | first=Garry | last=Maddox | date=24 November 2007 | accessdate=23 May 2010 | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200828/http://www.smh.com.au/news/film/filmmakers-take-on-hollywood-over-comedy-copy/2007/11/23/1195753303752.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 在《怪异同床人》制片人收到一份《我盛大的同志婚礼》的早期草稿证明抄袭不成立后，诉讼于2008年4月撤销。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/film/strange-fluke-not-plagiarism/2008/04/06/1207420193700.html |title=Strange fluke, not plagiarism - Film - Entertainment |newspaper=Sydney Morning Herald |date=6 April 2008 |accessdate=25 March 2011 |archive-date=2017-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419103628/http://www.smh.com.au/news/film/strange-fluke-not-plagiarism/2008/04/06/1207420193700.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

