==票房==
《怪异同床人》在澳大利亚票房4,816,495澳元，占2004年所有的澳洲电影票房的40%以上。电影获得了澳大利亚电影局颁发的票房成绩奖。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://film.vic.gov.au/resources/documents/AA4_Aust_Box_office_report.pdf |title=''Film Victoria - Australian Films at the Australian Box Office'' |access-date=2014-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110218045303/http://film.vic.gov.au/resources/documents/AA4_Aust_Box_office_report.pdf |archive-date=2011-02-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

